title: Bug 116564 - Hyperlink builder title changes with settings
OB: When reopening the hyperlink builder, its title becomes 'www.actuate.com'
EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', not 'www.actuate.com' based on the settings
SR:
1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'
2. Click on 'OK' to close the hyperlink builder
3. Reopen the hyperlink builder
